  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK493">
<l>āṟṟāru māṟṟi yaṭupa viṭaṉaṟintu </l>
<l>pōṟṟārkaṭ pōṟṟic ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even the powerless will become powerful and conquer, if they select a proper field (of action), and guard themselves, while they make war on their enemies.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
